{"id":276077,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-浙江省两会开幕，温州渔民递交诉求/","date":"2013-01-24T21:45:56Z","modified":"2013-01-24T21:45:56Z","title":"维权网 | 浙江省“两会”开幕，温州渔民递交诉求书（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员王若冲报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日上午</span><span>，浙江省政协十一届一次会议在浙江省人民大会堂开幕，官方媒体称“政协会议低调开幕，切实为民鼓与呼”。温州市洞县北岙镇小三盘村全体村民向省政协递交了《向省两会诉求书》，要求解决该村海涂被县政府非法侵占卖给开发商后遗留下来的问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>前洞头县副县长、小三盘村村民代言人林炳长代表村民向省两会提出了亟待解决的十二个问题：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、政府篡改《洞头县二期围垦许可证》，将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">284</span><span>公顷海涂面积改为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.84</span><span>公顷，以逃避国务院审批；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、政府非法将海涂卖给开发商搞房地产，十一年来使渔民失去生产资料和生活资料；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、省高级法院在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月已判决洞头县政府违法，但县政府迄今拒不执行判决；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>、要求政府对失地渔民解决失地保险问题；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>、要求政府对小三盘村渔民十一年来的的停产损失进行赔偿；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>、因诉讼是政府引起，又是政府败诉，要求政府承担</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>万元诉讼费用；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>、要求政府及开发商承担因炸山填海造成的撤离损失费；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>、要求平反冤假错案，赔偿杨玉秀、吕爱銮、林春莲、张孚端、黄明华、唐德烈、颜秀娟、张爱月等村民因维权被打、被关、被拘留、被劳教、被判刑的案子，并予以国家赔偿；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>、在颜秀娟一案中，派出所警察代为签名作假证，要求追究其刑事责任；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>、国家干部郑祥岁诈骗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>万元，村民实名举后却受到包庇，要求追究其刑事责任；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>、洞头县政府对抗十八大精神，要求追究其政治责任；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>、去年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日小山盘村民自发纪念毛泽东诞辰，政府却派人阻止并撕毁毛泽东像，要求追究其责任。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vE6l-vEQqYk/UQFEtLj4uBI/AAAAAAAAZ8w/rxHkYilnjFs/s1600/img177v.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vE6l-vEQqYk/UQFEtLj4uBI/AAAAAAAAZ8w/rxHkYilnjFs/s320/img177v.jpg\" width=\"224\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-nK5_2bKzZDo/UQFEvlMxqmI/AAAAAAAAZ84/E4gv4uuZ9Zs/s1600/img179v.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-nK5_2bKzZDo/UQFEvlMxqmI/AAAAAAAAZ84/E4gv4uuZ9Zs/s320/img179v.jpg\" width=\"224\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-PR_yvFJzR44/UQFEwgGupRI/AAAAAAAAZ88/HruuahNZwzY/s1600/img182.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-PR_yvFJzR44/UQFEwgGupRI/AAAAAAAAZ88/HruuahNZwzY/s320/img182.jpg\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-RSxZSmDqz_w/UQFExv1zi9I/AAAAAAAAZ9E/UqeitzsKcjY/s1600/img183.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-RSxZSmDqz_w/UQFExv1zi9I/AAAAAAAAZ9E/UqeitzsKcjY/s320/img183.jpg\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}